            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "heading_html": "<p>Procuring Open Infrastructure</p>",
          "body_html": "<p>Transitioning to open hardware can feel daunting, but you do not need to overhaul your entire operation overnight. <br><br>Join Matty in the video below, to learn how industry leaders approach adoption and why the journey often begins with a <strong>single step</strong>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#f2f2f2",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p>The&nbsp;<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.opencompute.org/marketplace\"><strong>OCP Marketplace</strong></a> is your central hub for finding <strong>recognized hardware</strong>, <strong>software</strong>, and <strong>facilities</strong>. It is not just a catalog; it is a vital tool for connecting with <strong>Solution Providers</strong> who can help you integrate <strong>open technology</strong> into your specific environment. <br><br>Whether you need <strong>ORv3 racks</strong> or a <strong>full solution</strong>, the marketplace ensures you are working with trusted, verified vendors.</p><p>Click on the markers to learn more about each segment.</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "labeled_graphic",
          "variant": "labeledgraphic",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#f2f2f2",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "media_width": "1",
            "media_width_variant": "medium"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "title": "Artificial Intelligence",
              "x": "14.449988313862477",
              "y": "51.306707619209966",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>Features cutting-edge hardware and infrastructure solutions optimized for AI workloads, including accelerators, liquid-cooling solutions and facilities designed to support scalable and energy-efficient AI deployments.</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "Integrated Solutions and Professional Services",
              "x": "32.44241633087894",
              "y": "51.41149216149685",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>End-to-end solutions utilizing OCP recognized hardware enhance operational efficiency across the data center. Professional services and products support sustainable deployment of infrastructure based on OCP standards.</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "Data Center Facilities & Experience Centers",
              "x": "50.18552875695733",
              "y": "52.2189349112426",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>OCP Ready™ self-certified data center facilities provide colocation services for hyperscale requirements. The primary focus of an OCP Experience Center is to accelerate open innovation and facilitate the widespread adoption of OCP-recognized equipment by showing it to visitors.</p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "Products",
              "x": "67.71799628942486",
              "y": "52.366863905325445",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>Showcases a diverse array of OCP recognized hardware designed to meet the needs of modern data centers including high-performance servers, storage systems, networking equipment, optics, rack and power equipment and much more.</p><p></p>"
            },
            {
              "title": "Chiplets",
              "x": "85.15769944341372",
              "y": "52.071005917159766",
              "icon": "01",
              "description_html": "<p>Advanced modular semiconductor components designed to enhance performance and flexibility in chip design including Ready-made Chiplets, IP, EDA, Design, Test and Foundries.</p><p></p>"
            }
          ],
          "media": {
