        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "heading_paragraph",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "heading_html": "<p>Steps to Deployment</p>",
          "body_html": "<p>Adopting open infrastructure is a strategic process. <br><br>Follow these key steps to ensure a smooth transition:</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "process",
          "variant": "process",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1c1c1c",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3,
            "media_width": "1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "intro",
              "title": "Introduction",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>Discover the essential steps to adopt and implement the framework effectively. Follow these guidelines to ensure a smooth transition and optimal results.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "Assess",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>Evaluate your current <strong>workloads</strong>, <strong>power limitations</strong>, and <strong>thermal challenges</strong> to understand your starting point and identify areas for improvement.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "Identify",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>Utilize the <strong>OCP Marketplace</strong> to locate <strong>hardware solutions</strong> that align with your specific <strong>density</strong> and <strong>operational requirements</strong>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "Partner",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>Collaborate with an <strong>OCP Solution Provider</strong> to develop a comprehensive <strong>integration plan</strong> tailored to your needs.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "step",
              "title": "Deploy",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>Begin with a <strong>small-scale implementation</strong>, such as a <strong>single rack</strong> or <strong>pilot pod</strong>, before expanding to a <strong>full facility deployment</strong>.</p>"
            },
            {
              "type": "summary",
              "title": "Conclusion",
              "hidden": false,
              "description_html": "<p>By following these steps, you can effectively adopt the framework and achieve your goals with confidence and efficiency.</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
